      "description": "Solid, dependable transportation with plenty of practical value left. This car is in fair condition, showing visible cosmetic wear and signs of age, but it still starts, runs, and can serve well as an affordable daily driver for someone who wants usefulness over perfection. If you\u2019re looking for an honest vehicle at a reasonable price, this one is worth a look.",
