    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Exceptionally clean mint-condition example that presents beautifully throughout and should satisfy a buyer looking for a standout car. The body, paint, trim, and interior all show extremely well, with only the slightest signs of age or careful use, and it has the overall appearance of a car that has been very well preserved. A buyer can expect a highly presentable, well-kept vehicle that feels special right away and is ready to be enjoyed as-is.",
