    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and priced to move, this vehicle offers dependable basic transportation for the right buyer. It shows its age and is best suited for someone seeking an inexpensive daily driver, project car, or backup vehicle. A practical opportunity to get on the road at a very accessible price.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of potential? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a solid opportunity for someone who wants a cheap daily, a first car, or a project to tinker with. It\u2019s priced right for the condition and offers a lot of value for the money. If you\u2019re realistic and want something budget-friendly that can still do a job, this could be a great fit. Come have a look and see if it suits what you need.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Budget-friendly driver/project with strong enthusiast appeal. This car shows its age cosmetically and will need attention, but the chassis still feels like a worthwhile platform and the powertrain presents as a usable starting point for someone who knows their way around maintenance and sorting. Ideal for a mechanically minded buyer looking for affordable entry, parts value, or a restoration candidate with good fundamentals. Priced to move and well worth a look if you want something inexpensive with real upside.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap entry car. Rough around the edges, priced to sell fast. Solid value for the money.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "A true diamond-in-the-rough, this car has the kind of presence that makes you look back after parking it. It wears its miles like a well-loved leather jacket\u2014full of character, stories, and unmistakable personality. For the right buyer, it\u2019s an affordable gateway into ownership: a dependable canvas for a project, a practical runabout, or a budget-friendly ride with plenty of life and charm left to give. If you appreciate cars with soul and see possibility where others see age, this one is ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
